#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "MOD to grow tea leaves"
msgstr "种植茶叶的MOD"

#. ~ Description for MOD to grow tea leaves
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds new tea leaf seeds and raw tea leaves crafting options, new types of "
"tea leaves and tea."
msgstr "添加新的茶叶种子和生茶叶制作选项，以及新型茶叶和茶饮。"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "sugarless tea"
msgid_plural "sugarless tea"
msgstr[0] "无糖茶"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "fruit tea"
msgid_plural "fruit tea"
msgstr[0] "水果茶"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "decaffeinated tea"
msgid_plural "decaffeinated teas"
msgstr[0] "脱咖啡因茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'decaffeinated tea'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"It is a tea extracted with water. It is safe to drink before going to bed "
"because caffeine is significantly reduced, but it may not be enough because "
"the taste has changed compared to those made with hot water."
msgstr "这是一种用水萃取的茶。由于咖啡因含量显著降低，睡前饮用是安全的，但味道与热水冲泡的茶相比有所变化，可能不够满足。"

#: .\tl_drink.json .\tl_materials.json
msgid "green tea"
msgid_plural "green teas"
msgstr[0] "绿茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'green tea'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"Green tea is a tea made from tea leaves, which is processed by heating the "
"picked tea leaves to prevent fermentation. Vivid fresh green is beautiful."
msgstr "绿茶是由茶叶制成的茶，通过加热采摘的茶叶以防止发酵处理而成。鲜艳的嫩绿色泽十分美丽。"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "decaffeinated green tea"
msgid_plural "decaffeinated green teas"
msgstr[0] "脱咖啡因绿茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'decaffeinated green tea'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"水で抽出した緑茶です。カフェインが大幅に少なくなっているので就寝前に飲用しても安心ですが、お湯で作ったものよりも味が変化しているので物足りないかもしれません。"
msgstr "这是一种用水萃取的绿茶。由于咖啡因含量大幅减少，睡前饮用也很安心，但味道与热水冲泡的相比有所变化，可能不够满足。"

#: .\tl_drink.json .\tl_materials.json
msgid "oolong tea"
msgid_plural "oolong teas"
msgstr[0] "乌龙茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'oolong tea'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"Oolong tea is a semi-fermented tea that is classified as blue tea among "
"Chinese teas and stopped fermentation by heating during fermentation of tea "
"leaves. I will refresh after drinking after meals."
msgstr "乌龙茶是一种半发酵茶，在中国茶中属于青茶类，通过在茶叶发酵过程中加热停止发酵。餐后饮用能提神醒脑。"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "decaffeinated oolong tea"
msgid_plural "decaffeinated oolong teas"
msgstr[0] "脱咖啡因乌龙茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'decaffeinated oolong tea'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"It is oolong tea extracted with water. It is safe to drink before going to "
"bed, as caffeine is significantly reduced, but the taste may have changed "
"and more than those made with hot water."
msgstr "这是一种用水萃取的乌龙茶。由于咖啡因含量显著降低，睡前饮用是安全的，但味道可能已改变，且比热水冲泡的更浓郁。"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "boiled plum tea"
msgid_plural "boiled plum teas"
msgstr[0] "煮梅茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boiled plum tea'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"Sumomo simmered with black tea and sugar. The sweetness of the tea is good "
"and the flavor of the tea is good."
msgstr "用红茶和糖炖煮的李子。茶的甜度恰到好处，茶香浓郁。"

#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid "milk tea with banana and chocolate flavorings"
msgid_plural "milk tea with banana and chocolate flavoringss"
msgstr[0] "香蕉巧克力风味奶茶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'milk tea with banana and chocolate flavorings'}
#: .\tl_drink.json
msgid ""
"It has a sweet, rich, parfait-like flavor with a milk-rich black tea plus "
"banana and chocolate flavors."
msgstr "这是一种甜味浓郁、类似芭菲风味的饮品，以奶香浓郁的红茶为基础，加入香蕉和巧克力风味。"

